snippet: A Taliban suicide bomber rammed a truck packed with explosives into a compound housing a paramilitary force in Karachi on Thursday, killing 3 officers and wounding 20.
abstract: Taliban suicide bomber rams truck packed with explosives into compound housing paramilitary force in Karachi, Pakistan, killing 3 officers and wounding 20.
lead_paragraph: A Taliban suicide bomber rammed a truck packed with explosives into a compound housing a paramilitary force in Karachi on Thursday, killing 3 officers and wounding 20.
